metadata.name: I'm Alive
metadata.description:
I'm alive!

Acrylic on paper

It's a burst of freshness  
The dawn of a new season  
Colours and beauty fills the sky  
Greyness faded with the nights

Yesterday's a passing shadow  
The morrow is full of hope and of life.  
Hey! I'm alive!  
Isn't that a beautiful song to be sung?
